{"tid":1896813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知名越南髮型屋　迷你裙美女「皇帝級服務」僅50港元客似雲來","createTime":"2020-02-25T10:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T13:06:32.000Z","uid":297241,"like":17,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"51b0fb6b3429a4b7e14114d1a1990874e91dddc7","tid":1896813,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"知名越南髮型屋　<br />\n迷你裙美女「皇帝級服務」<br />\n僅50港元客似雲來<br />\n<br />\n來到越南河內的女生喜歡做美甲，那男生千萬別錯過傳說中的洗頭店。日前一間理髮店的內部照在網路上瘋傳，仔細一看<span style=\"color: red;\">並非一般的理髮店，店內的女設計師都擁有姣好臉蛋與曼妙身材，</span>且全套剪髮還包括全身按摩、敷臉、洗腳、修指甲、剃鬍、掏耳朵，含小費價位卻只需要約港幣50元，讓人忍不住直呼：「頭好癢！」<br />\n<br />\n越南的美容業相當發達，內行遊客到了當地不可不拜訪的便是理髮店。越南粉專《Ph&ograve;ng trọ của những Hot girl》日前分享當地理髮院「30shine」照片，只見<span style=\"color: red;\">店內設計師全是穿著白色上衣、黑色貼身短裙的正妹，襯托出身材相當凹凸有緻</span>，正在細心的幫客人洗頭"},{"pid":"2d56496b8b0d1cb5fd0c90c171433801ffe87271","tid":1896813,"uid":297241,"like":9,"dislike":11,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T10:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e436e89a5e2c82bd609635a.jpg/vXhwpGgzg26w_12Pi8D5Op3E4qavkzItOnbt_Dp27fw?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e436e89a5e2c82bd609635a.jpg%2FvXhwpGgzg26w_12Pi8D5Op3E4qavkzItOnbt_Dp27fw%3Fv%3Dw800&h=fdd31c2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"426e7ac841d6c2b31acff0a34e60094f27187e14","tid":1896813,"uid":297241,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T10:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e436e76fe36d22bbeb15699.jpg/j0X8hTVFTsZFNKEfJdM7qaMqW3sbJGahKLrkBSi65AU?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e436e76fe36d22bbeb15699.jpg%2Fj0X8hTVFTsZFNKEfJdM7qaMqW3sbJGahKLrkBSi65AU%3Fv%3Dw800&h=fe227476&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"495b399c492e44b0755acd0574c1a50037577895","tid":1896813,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-